# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok new british foreign secretary david miliband made his first trip to paris wednesday to discuss key challenges including eu reform and reviving the middle east peace process .
# ::alignments
(t / trip-03
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "David"
                  :op2 "Miliband")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Britain"))
                  :ARG2 (s / secretary
                        :topic (f / foreign)))
            :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01))
      :ARG1 c
      :name (n4 / name
            :op1 "Paris")
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :purpose (d / discuss-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (c2 / challenge-01
                  :ARG1-of (k / key-02)
                  :ARG2-of (ii / include-91
                        :ARG1 (a / and
                              :op1 (r / reform-01
                                    :ARG1 (o / organization
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "EU")))
                              :op2 (r2 / revive-01
                                    :ARG1 (p2 / process-02
                                          :ARG1 (p3 / peace)
                                          :location (w2 / world-region
                                                :name (n6 / name
                                                      :op1 "Middle"
                                                      :op2 "East")))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok at least ## people were feared dead sunday when a bus they were traveling in skidded off a road and plunged into a fast-flowing river in indian kashmir , police said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / police)
      :ARG1 (f / fear-01
            :ARG1 (d / die-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :quant (a / at-least
                              :op1 1)))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))
            :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (s3 / skid-01
                              :ARG1 (b / bus
                                    :ARG1-of (t / travel-01
                                          :ARG0 p2))
                              :ARG2 (o / off
                                    :op1 (r / road)))
                        :op2 (p3 / plunge-01
                              :ARG1 b
                              :ARG4 (r2 / river
                                    :ARG1-of (f2 / flow-01
                                          :ARG1-of (f3 / fast-02))
                                    :location (c2 / country
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "India"))))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the united nations high commissioner for refugees -lrb- unhcr -rrb- has donated one million us dollars to iran to prepare for the probable flood of iraqi refugees , unhcr spokesman in iran mohammad nouri said on friday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Mohammad"
                  :op2 "Nouri")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (o / organization
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "Nations"
                              :op3 "High"
                              :op4 "Commission"
                              :op5 "for"
                              :op6 "Refugees"))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / spokesman))
            :location (c / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Iran")))
      :ARG1 (d / donate-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000
                  :unit (d2 / dollar
                        :mod c
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "US"))))
      :ARG2 c
      :purpose (p2 / prepare-02
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG2 (f / flood-01
                  :ARG2 (r / refugee
                        :mod c
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Iraq")))
            :mod (p3 / probable))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG1 (h2 / home
            :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01)
            :beneficiary (n3 / nato
                  :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)
                  :ARG1-of (c / capable-01
                        :ARG2 (t / tackle-01
                              :ARG0 n3
                              :ARG1 (c2 / challenge-01
                                    :mod (g2 / globe)
                                    :example (a / and
                                          :op1 (t2 / terrorism)
                                          :op2 (p2 / piracy)
                                          :op3 (w / warfare
                                                :mod (c3 / cyber)))))))
            :domain (b / building
                  :poss m
                  :mod (h3 / headquarters)
                  :mod (m2 / massive)
                  :ARG1-of (n5 / new-01))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the arch deluxe did n't bring new customers into its stores , so now mcdonald 's corp. appears poised to try something old -- price cutting .
# ::alignments
(b / bring-01
      :polarity -
      :ARG0 (p / product
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Arch"
                  :op2 "deluxe"))
      :ARG1 (c / customer
            :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01))
      :ARG2 (s / store
            :poss p)
      :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (a / appear-02
                  :ARG1 (p2 / poise-01
                        :ARG1 (c3 / corporation
                              :poss (c4 / company
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "McDonald's")))
                        :ARG2 (t / try-01
                              :ARG0 c3
                              :ARG1 (c5 / cut-02
                                    :ARG0 c3
                                    :ARG1 (p3 / price-01)
                                    :mod (o / old))))
                  :time (n4 / now))))

                                    :polarity -)

                                          :op1 "Worldcom"))))

                        :mod (s4 / shock-01))
                  :ARG2 (s5 / sector))))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :op2 "Akbulut")

                  :mod (r2 / religious-group
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Turk"))

                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Rey"
                                    :op2 "Eduardo")
                              :ARG0-of (b / box-03)
                              :mod c)
                        :subevent-of (g / game
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "World"
                                    :op2 "Championship")
                              :mod (b2 / box-03)
                              :location (c2 / country
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "Italy")))))
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (t / tough-03
                        :ARG1 p)
                  :ARG3 (m / more)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w / wednesday)))

                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)
                  :time (f / former))

                  :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Congress"))
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :month 1))
            :ARG0-of (l / live-01
                  :location (e / exile-01)))
      :ARG4 (h2 / home)
      :time d
      :weekday (f2 / friday)
      :purpose (t / try-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (r2 / retake-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p3 / power)))
      :concession-of (a / arrest-01
            :ARG1 p
            :time (a2 / arrive-01
                  :ARG1 p)))
